Periscope is Twitter's new iPhone app that allows users to broadcast live video and audio to the internet . 
  App developer Justin Esgar is warning parents about the 'land mines' in the app . 
  Users have reported that they have been sexually harassed or trolled while using it . 
  One woman reported that the app allowed her to be stalked by a male friend . 
  The app also enabled users to share their location with other users . 
  It launched last Thursday . 
 